# Defense in depth.
#
# Personal data: PM profile lives at ~/.initiative-creator/ (outside this
# repo); initiative-*.md files live in the PM's chosen CWD (also outside
# this repo). These rules block both at this plugin's repo root in case
# of an accidental copy. Files under templates/ are explicitly preserved
# by the leading-slash anchoring below.

/profile.md
/initiative-*.md
.initiative-creator/

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
